data.name: 0000 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Look! Doesn't the corridor seem kind of strange?

data.name: 0001 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Huh? D-does it?

data.name: 0002 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's deeeefinitely strange!

data.name: 0003 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: It's weirdly dark and the atmosphere feels kind of different from normal!

data.name: 0004 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: So it wasn't just my imagination…

data.name: 0005 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Let's hurry, Mikuru!

data.name: 0006 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Eek, wait for meee—

data.name: 0007 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: S-Suzumiya!

data.name: 0008 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What is it all of a sudden, Mikuru?

data.name: 0009 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Umm, the… The truth about class 1-10 is… Umm, let me explain the trick…

data.name: 0010 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: H-huh? What was I supposed to do here…? …Eeek.

data.name: 0011 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What are you doing there by yourself, Mikuru?

data.name: 0012 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: No it's, umm, it's…

data.name: 0013 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If you don't need me I'll just go off ahead.

data.name: 0014 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Oh, wait! Th-this!

data.name: 0015 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hm? What's this? This is the plate for class 6, isn't it?

data.name: 0016 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Where'd you find this?

data.name: 0017 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Umm… I-it had fallen on the floor!

data.name: 0018 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Fallen? This plate?

data.name: 0019 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Y-yes.

data.name: 0020 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hmm…

data.name: 0021 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I don't really see how it could've fallen…

data.name: 0022 (540.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Something's kind of bothering me though.

data.name: 0023 (540.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Eeeek…
